highlights.text: “Baby, I'm Jealous (feat. Doja Cat)” by Bebe Rexha and Doja Cat is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #109.
BLACKPINK has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Lovesick Girls” is the highest at #18.
“Shape of You” by Ed Sheeran has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 197 weeks straight.
“Mi Niña” by Wisin, Myke Towers, and Los Legendarios is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 94 spots at #99.
